headline: Joby Aviation (JOBY) Sees 125% Stock Price Increase Over Last Quarter
summary: Joby Aviation (JOBY) demonstrated a 125% increase in stock price over the last quarter, highlighting a period marked by significant events. The successful piloted flight of its eVTOL air taxi between U.S. airports in FAA-controlled airspace on August 15 was pivotal, showcasing its operational readiness for the commercial market. Additionally, forming a joint venture with ANA Holdings to launch air taxi services in Japan and partnering with L3Harris Technologies to develop hybrid VTOL aircraft...
